 THE Federal Capital Territory (FCT) Ministerial Task Force on City Sanitation on Thursday raided a notorious drug colony in Abuja, arresting four dealers. The task force also raided another drug den in Games Village, where it made some more arrests, The Nation learnt Police in Kano have arrested 1,583 suspected drug dealers and thugs in the past eight months in the state, it was gathered. Commissioner of Police Habu Ahmad stated this in a statement signed by the spokesman of the command, DSP Abdullahi Haruna yesterday in Kano.